main event: Luminous objects traveling at supersonic speeds were observed and tracked on radar in the Pork Chop and Old Baldy Hills area of Korea.
interesting points: Two luminous objects were reported to be traveling at speeds of up to 600 mph and possibly exceeding 1800 mph., The objects were tracked via ground radar., Significant military communications were involved, indicating a heightened interest in the sightings., Multiple reports suggested that various luminous objects had been observed over a few days., There was insufficient data for a proper evaluation of the sightings.
location: Pork Chop and Old Baldy Hills, Korea
